DESCRIPTION OF THIS PROGRAM: ----------------------------

- SAY2RAW use the SAY command (SYS:UTILITIES/SAY) from the Workbench.
  SAY2RAW works exactly like the SAY command.



INTRODUCTION: ------------- SAY2RAW convert the speech output from the Amiga
into RAWDATAS. A BLUE SCREEN indicates a buffer oveflow! (Buffer = 100000
Bytes)



USAGE: ------

Say2Raw [say option] TEXT


EXAMPLE: --------

Say2Raw -r -p65 this is a test

